cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.SE, cs.AI, cs.DC

The paper discusses the detection of botnets in networks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network security (cs.NI). The use of honeypots and automated malware collection and analysis also involves software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the infrastructure required for collecting and correlating data involves distributed computing (cs.DC).
